%N A354222 Decimal expansion of 2 / (Pi+2).
%C A354222 The sequence u(n+1) = 1 / ( u(n) + 1/(n+1) ) with u(0) >= 0 is convergent with lim_{n->oo} u(n) = 1; however, this sequence is monotonic iff u(0) = 2 / (Pi+2), and in this case, this sequence is increasing.
